<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.5">
<l>pañcavar tūtaṉāyp pārataṅ kaiceytu</l>
<l>nañcumiḻ nākaṅ kiṭantanal poykaipuk</l>
<l>kañcap paṇattiṉmēl pāyntiṭ ṭaruḷceyta</l>
<l>vañcaṉa vaṇṇaṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">vacōtai taṉciṅkattaip pāṭippaṟa.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the kohl coloured one who,</l>
<l rend="indent">as a messenger to the Five, assited in the Bhārata war,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and,] having entered the good pond</l>
<l rend="indent">where dwelt a snake spitting poison</l>
<l>showed grace, leaping on [its] hood so that it was afraid.</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the lion of Yaśodā!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
